{"tid":560050,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【星期三】聽日自己一個可以去邊好","createTime":"2018-02-13T17:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T05:21:26.000Z","uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2731f66b99edd43852a270be22e5f191924a305f","tid":560050,"uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"我同自己講聽日都係星期三咪又係咁過，但呢個星期無論出街行，留係屋企上網，都比情人節嘅氣氛影響到。<br />\n個人好灰鳩，去買衫都覺得自己著乜都咁柒(雖然可能係真)<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日決定集思廣益安排個驚世節目比自己。<br />\n<br />\n有諗過出去影相，但好驚影影下有情侶走埋黎問我可唔可以。。。。<br />\n有諗過去海洋公園玩(有張免費飛)<br />\n有諗過去網吧過一日<br />\n有諗過約下女仔。。。但咁遲先約搵鬼睬我。<br />\n<br />\n巴打，係時間集思廣益❗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9b4a1cdb6355252fd12555d8a10d363c722c88","tid":560050,"uid":152437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1844469995a8a18c69ee6fdfc96dbe95d67dea3c","tid":560050,"uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a9b4a1cdb6355252fd12555d8a10d363c722c88","tid":560050,"uid":152437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"韓燒我會啱啲，唱K老牛聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa843b5830c68d19e33264a692c54043e82f0c8","tid":560050,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cff90e402a2b256df2a3975fcaa5cd6eaf24a93","tid":560050,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T22:56:02.000Z","msg":"吉野家打個邊爐囉"},{"pid":"0fb32927c3b984b23d1d1de09a42742c099ee772","tid":560050,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,